{
  "stem": "2684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we get off on the left-hand side on the platform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And SS with dogs, uniforms, soldiers all around on the other side of the platform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And all we heard is [SPEAKING GERMAN] which means, move, move, going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we started moving on the platform to a certain point, the top of the platform.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you couldn't see much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Only on the above, I saw the sign that 'Arbeit Macht Frei.' And there was no name of Auschwitz or anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was day time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mentality, even as a child, was shattered of the two days, two and a half days trip that I didn't know day, night.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I knew, it was light because end of the line stood a man, a high officer, extremely good looking, extremely well dressed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember his face, powder on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When a man shaved in those days, he put powder after the shaving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a very vicious dog in his-- in his-- on the leash.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody who walked have to walk in front of him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was standing there with a few other officers, smaller officer, but he was the head guy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had these four, five friends of mine with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this best friend of mine, Banja Ferica, he was smaller than I am.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was not as wise, streetwise, as I am.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And came the sign, which I told previously that, God gave me something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was well built.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was a sportsman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I pulled my chest up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I flexed my muscles in front of him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Either I wanted to show that I am a man, or I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And with his finger like this, he showed me, go to the right.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
